thread.title: Antoinette
thread.title_full: Fast Cover Travel Insurance reviewed by Antoinette

author: Antoinette
title: Antoinette
text: It was easy for me to buy the policy , I recieved a Quote: at first , then I phoned and spoke to a very pleasant lady on the phone and the transaction went quickly. I did not have to claim so I don't know how quick they are to pay if you need to claim.. All the documentation I received seemed comprehensive.
